            <p>
              Our wedding ceremony & reception will take place at the beautiful Dreams Las Mareas Resort in Costa Rica. We will also have a small reception in NJ for those who cannot make the trip. For more information, <a href="#reception" aria-controls="reception" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">click here.</a>
