            <h2>Flights</h2>
            <h5>Liberia, Costa Rica (LIR)</h5>
            <p>
              Flights from EWR or JFK can range from $300 - $450 round trip. I would suggest searching on <a href="http://www.skyscanner.com" target="_blank">Skyscanner</a> or <a href="http://www.momondo.com" target="_blank">Momondo</a>.
            </p>

              <div id="tips" class='row'>
                <ul class='col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3 col-xs-12'>
                <h5>Tips on getting a good price...</h5>
                  <li>Set up price alerts.</li>
                  <li>Book your flight between 4 months and 6 weeks before.</li>
                  <li>Best day & time to shop is Tuesday around 3pm. This is when airlines release the most sales.</li>
                  <li>Depart on a Tuesday or Wednesday.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <p>For more details, take a look <a href="http://www.farecompare.com/travel-advice/tips-from-air-travel-insiders/#/" target='_blank'>here</a> and <a href="http://thriftynomads.com/booking-cheapest-flight-possible-anywhere/" target='_blank'>here</a>.</p>
          </div>
